data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Motivated Sellers! Your search is over! A stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath home with a fireplace is exactly what you have been looking for! Located in the heart of Tampa this home is move-in ready for you to enjoy and host your next gathering. This magnificent property sits on a 75 x 200-foot extra-deep oversized lot that seamlessly blends luxury and relaxation. Bring your toys, boat, RV, etc. stress-free with no worry of HOA. Enjoy a dedicated covered space for parking in addition to a two-car garage. With a spacious 2,591 sq ft interior, this residence offers plenty of room to make yourself feel right at home. A fresh coat of paint refreshes the exterior and compliments the tile roof. The main living spaces radiate warmth and elegance providing the perfect scenery for both entertaining and quiet evenings with loved ones. Enjoy cooking meals in the modern open kitchen. A tasteful layout guides you through the open-concept area, seamlessly connecting the living and dining areas. The master suite is a true sanctuary, offering relaxation with its spacious layout and master bath whirlpool jacuzzi perfect for settling down after a long day. Three additional bedrooms with one of them being an additional master provide ample space for family, guests, or a dedicated home office. Conveniently located with easy access to I-275, highly rated schools, the University of South Florida (USF), VA & Florida Hospitals, diverse dining, retail, places of worship, Tampa International Airport, Raymond James Stadium, beaches, and the dynamics sought after Tampa community. Call today for your private showing. Sellers can accommodate a quick closing.
